it.apice.sapere.api.ecolaws.impl
Class ChemicalPatternImpl<ExtenderType>

java.lang.Object
  it.apice.sapere.api.ecolaws.impl.ChemicalPatternImpl<ExtenderType>
Type Parameters:
ExtenderType - Final type of the pattern (Product or Reactant), used as a trick for chaining. Its adoption requires the suppression of unchecked since, at runtime, it's not possible to check against a generic type.
All Implemented Interfaces:
ChemicalPattern<ExtenderType>
Direct Known Subclasses:
